title: Who Supports Free Trade?
description:
What are predictors of pro or anti-free trade sentiment? This video discusses data from the paper "Why are Some People (and Countries) more Protectionist than Others?" by Anna Maria Mayda and Dani Rodrik. This video also covers which countries are the most and least pro-free trade, how men and women view trade free trade differently, and how factors models come into play.
